                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160214-98-off573 t18160214-98-cd574"></join>, six tea-spoons, value 14s. two table spoons, value 20s. and one pair of sugar tongs, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18160214-98-victim1046" type="victimName">
                  Mary Ann 
                  Nixon
               <interp inst="t18160214-98-victim1046" type="surname" value="Nixon"></interp>
